high_descs: Turn left head towards the wall, turn right towards the edge of the table, and then turn left to face the white bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl next to the stove.
Turn right towards coffee maker and then turn right towards the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the bowl next to the bottom tomato, close the fridge fro the bowl to cool down, and take out the bowl from the fridge.
Turn left to face the dishwasher.
Open the cabinet to the right of the dishwasher and place the bowl in it.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled bowl in the cabinet next to the dishwasher.

high_descs: Walk to the stove on the left side of the room.
Pick up the square container that is next to the stove.
Turn around and walk around the kitchen island to the refrigerator on the other side of the room.
Place the container on the middle shelf of the fridge, shut the door, and take the container back out after two seconds.
Turn left and face the cabinets on the right of the sink.
Open the cabinet furthest to the right and place the container inside.
anns.task_desc: Place chilled container in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the plastic bowl on the kitchen counter.
Pick up  the plastic bowl off of the kitchen counter.
Turn right and walk over to the coffee machine, then hang a right and continue forward., then hang another right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the plastic bowl inside then close the fridge door, after a few seconds open the fridge door and remove the plastic bow, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk up to the kitchen counter.
Open the farthest right cabinet door that is right in front of you, place the chilled plastic bowl inside, and close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled plastic bowl inside a kitchen cabinet.
